'Yan majalisar Welsh sun yi tir da raba wa'yan takarar
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun yi fargaba da sauya sunan su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya zo ne saboda akwai shirin canza sunan zuwa Welsh Parliament.
Mutanen siyasa suna damuwa da yadda za a iya samun kudi daga gare su.
Wani dan majalisar wakilai ya nuna cewa kungiyarsa tana tsoron cewa zai yi rijista da Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje Wales: A cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin raba, kuma pwp yana nufin shitty.
Wani jami'in Plaid ya ce kungiyar ta kasance mai tsattsauran ra'ayi, kuma ta yi la'akari da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani daga cikin Conservative Party ya ce kungiyarsa ta kasance "ba ta da wata hujja" game da canjin sunan, amma ya yi sharhi cewa ya kasance ɗan gajeren lokaci daga MWP zuwa Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, ana amfani da harafin Welsh w a cikin hanyar da harafin u ya yi amfani da shi a cikin Yorkshire Turanci.
Majalisar dattawa, wanda a halin yanzu ke tattare da majalisar dokoki don aiwatar da canjin sunan, ya yanke hukunci kamar haka: Abin da ya kamata a yanke shawara game da kalmomin da za a yi amfani da majalisar dattijai, za a yanke shi ne daga cikin mambobin kansu.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba Majalisar Welsh ikon canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya sanar da sakamakon shawarwarin da aka yi game da wannan batu, inda aka ce yawancin 'yan majalisar sun goyi bayan a sake nada majalisar a matsayin Welsh Parliament.
A cikin batun batun 'yan majalisa, an kira shi Welsh Parliament Members ko WMP, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi kyau a cikin shawarwari na jama'a.
'Yan majalisar sun nuna wasu hanyoyin, amma gwagwarmayar cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama babban batun shugaban majalisar, Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da wani kudurin doka kan sauye-sauyen a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar sake fasalin za ta kuma ƙunshi wasu canje-canje ga tsarin aikin majalisa, yanzu dokokin da suka shafi rashin daidaito na majalisa da kuma tsarin kwamiti.
'Yan majalisar sun yi zaɓe na ƙarshe kan abin da za su kira a lokacin da suke tattauna dokar.
