Muhimmancin tsayayyar manufofin tattalin arziki, tsaron kasa, Turai, rage yawan farashi, duk irin wadannan tambayoyi ne da Jeremy ya yi muhawara da su a tsakanin shugabannin da suka gabata.
Rahoton taron da aka yi a Nottingham East Labour ranar Juma'a, ya ci gaba da cewa  muna son taron ya kasance mai fa'ida da kuma kirkiro.
A cikin shekaru takwas da na yi a matsayin 'yar majalisar wakili ta Labour, taron majalisar a ranar Juma'a da yamma, shi ne abin da nake so.
Saboda haka, a yanzu, a cikin tarurruka da yawa, ba a jin sautin wannan, kuma alkawuran da aka yi game da wannan, musamman ma siyasar, an manta da su tun da daɗewa, idan ma sun fara.
A hankali ya zama sananne cewa ba a yarda da ra'ayoyi daban-daban a cikin Labour Party ba, kuma ana yanke hukunci akan duk ra'ayoyin dangane da ko sun dace da jagorancin jam'iyyar.
Wannan ya fara ne bayan Jeremy ya zama shugaba, lokacin da abokan aiki waɗanda na yi tunanin cewa ina da ra'ayin siyasa iri ɗaya da su suka fara tsammanin zan yi ta'aziyya kuma in nuna ra'ayoyin da ban taɓa yarda da su ba - yanzu game da batun ƙasa ko kuma batun cikin gida na Tarayyar Turai.
