Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani taron jama'a a Wheeling, West Virginia a wannan maraice.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan da Trump ya shirya gudanarwa a mako mai zuwa, inda zai tsaya a wurare da ya fi so a Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka rage barazanar zabensa na cike gurbin da ke kan kujerar kotun koli, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya don zaben na tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon majalisar yayin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Taron Trump a West Virginia yana gabatowa a daren yau kuma yaya kuke kallon layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, don 7 na yamma ET a ranar Asabar 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia kai tsaye a YouTube a kasa.
Trump na iya yin magana game da shari'ar da aka gabatar a kan Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a matsayin Babban Shari'a a wannan makon, wani mataki da aka dauka a kan batun cin zarafin mata, inda aka dakatar da wani hukuncin da aka yanke a majalisar dattawa na tsawon mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan rikici na neman zabe shi ne ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi takara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, a yayin da jam'iyyar Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan 'yan majalisun da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, tawagar Trump ta sanar da cewa za ta gudanar da wasu tarurruka biyar a mako mai zuwa don karfafa 'yan tawaye da magoya baya.
"Gudanar da majalisa yana da mahimmanci ga shirinsa na ba da izini, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu, duk lokacin da muka kusanci wani muhimmin lokaci", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki a ambaci sunansa, ya fada wa Reuters.
Taron da aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a daren yau zai iya tara masu tallafawa daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a yi ta ba da rahoto a kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, zai zama karo na biyu a cikin wata guda da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump ya yi kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Republican a majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke fama da takara.
"Ba kyakkyawan abu ba ne ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya karfafa shi a cikin za ~ en za ~ en, "in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
