Paul Barreira, malamin ilimin hauka a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban sashen kiwon lafiya a jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan kwas ɗin ne bayan da aka yi gargadin cewa ɗalibai suna fama da rashin barci.
