Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin barazana da labaran farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da wani babban jaridar kasar Sin ya wallafa wani dogon rubutu mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka, inda ya yi zargin cin zarafin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci a ranar Lahadi da ta gabata kan batun albashi na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi yawan sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ta zargi China da kokarin shiga cikin zaben wakilan Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Shugabannin Amurka sun shaida wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa, zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na kokarin yin kutse a zaben Amurka, wani sabon mataki ne da Washington ke dauka a yakin neman zabe, don matsawa China.
Duk da cewa gwamnatocin kasashen waje suna yin karin karin haske don kokarin bunkasa cinikayya, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin rikici na cinikayya, wanda ya haifar da hauhawar haraji kan shigo da kayayyaki daga kasashen biyu.
China ta dauki fansa a farkon yakin cinikayya don yanke 'yan ci-rani a jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayan aikin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta sanya haraji kan ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, ya rubuta Branstad a cikin wani ra'ayi a ranar Lahadi ta Des Moines Register, tsar da batun ta hanyar buga farfaganda bayani a cikin mu free latsa.
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandar da ake yi, China ta yi amfani da dabi'un Amurka, da 'yancin magana da' yancin 'yan jarida, ta hanyar buga labarai a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A wani kwatankwacin, a cikin gidajen jaridu a kan titin Beijing, za ka iya samun muryoyi masu rarrabuwa, masu rarrabewa da kuma ra'ayoyi marasa ma'ana game da ra'ayoyi daban-daban da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya samu game da rikitarwar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda kwaminis na jam'iyyar kwaminis na kasar Sin yana da iko a kan kafofin watsa labarai", ya rubuta.
Ya kara da cewa, daya daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da tayin da aka ba shi na buga sashensa, amma bai bayyana ko wane jarida ba ne.
