A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa da ta auku a garin Palu da ke kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'an gwamnati, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da rashin ingantattun hanyoyin sadarwa, ba a sami wani rahoto daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu, kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa, wanda ya kai 7.5 a ma'aunin Richter.
Fiye da mutane 16,000 ne suka yi hijira a birnin Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawest:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Mid Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, yana da yawan jama'a na 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A ranar 40 na birnin, an yi wata babbar biki, sai aka yi girgizar ƙasa kuma aka yi ambaliyar ruwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) na gabar teku a wani yanki a tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin jihar, wanda a zahiri yana ƙarƙashin wani yanki, yawan jama'a ya kai 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Fishing da noma ne manyan kayayyaki na tattalin arzikin yankin a tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Nikkulnám ma yana da mahimmanci a cikin yankin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen gabar Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsanani a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma mamaye Yammacin Tsakiya a 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana kan yankin girgizar kasa na Pacific kuma a kai a kai ana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa a zamanin da:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a Arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami, wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane sama da 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A jerin girgizar kasa da girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afka yammacin gabar Sumatra a karshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda ta haifar da tsunami da ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, nesa da Sumatra, inda ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai girman mita 10, wadda ta lalata garuruwa da dama tare da kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Aceh, inda ta yi sanadiyyar lalacewa da fargaba, tun da mutane sun tuna da lalacewar da aka yi a 2004 da kuma tsunami.
Babu wanda ya mutu a wannan karon, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu sakamakon rushewar gine-ginen.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia inda mutane fiye da 500 suka mutu, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata gine-gine da yawa kuma ta sa dubban mutane suka makale.
